data.description: Welcome to a rare opportunity to own a sprawling estate set on 12.2 acres of land. This expansive property boasts the potential for a grand and luxurious residence, offering a remarkable 11 bedrooms for unparalleled space and flexibility. Nestled within the natural beauty of its surroundings, this home presents an ideal canvas for those with a vision for restoration and customization.  The vast acreage provides privacy and seclusion, creating a serene retreat for those seeking a tranquil lifestyle. Majestic trees, including Maple trees, and open spaces set the stage for outdoor activities and the creation of a private oasis.  Opportunities like this are rare, and for those with the creativity and determination to undertake a rehabilitation project, this estate represents a chance to create a dream residence or Air B&B in a truly idyllic setting. Embrace the challenge, unlock the potential, and make this expansive property your own sanctuary for years to come!
